@startuml OpiumProtocol_opium-protocol-v2

actor User
participant "Core" as Core
participant "Registry" as Registry
participant "SyntheticAggregator" as SyntheticAggregator
participant "OracleAggregator" as OracleAggregator
participant "OpiumProxyFactory" as OpiumProxyFactory
participant "TokenSpender" as TokenSpender
participant "PositionToken" as PositionToken

User -> Core: Create derivative position
activate Core

Core -> Registry: Check permissions
Registry --> Core: Permissions granted

Core -> SyntheticAggregator: Get derivative details
SyntheticAggregator --> Core: Return derivative info

Core -> OpiumProxyFactory: Create position tokens
OpiumProxyFactory -> PositionToken: Deploy LONG and SHORT tokens
PositionToken --> OpiumProxyFactory: Tokens created
OpiumProxyFactory --> Core: Return token addresses

Core -> TokenSpender: Transfer margin
TokenSpender -> User: Request token approval
User --> TokenSpender: Approve tokens
TokenSpender --> Core: Margin transferred

Core --> User: Position created

deactivate Core

...Time passes...

User -> Core: Settle derivative
activate Core

Core -> OracleAggregator: Fetch settlement price
OracleAggregator --> Core: Return price data

Core -> SyntheticAggregator: Calculate payout
SyntheticAggregator --> Core: Return payout amounts

Core -> TokenSpender: Distribute payouts
TokenSpender -> User: Transfer payout
TokenSpender --> Core: Payout distributed

Core -> OpiumProxyFactory: Burn position tokens
OpiumProxyFactory -> PositionToken: Burn LONG and SHORT tokens
PositionToken --> OpiumProxyFactory: Tokens burned
OpiumProxyFactory --> Core: Tokens burned confirmation

Core --> User: Settlement complete

deactivate Core

@enduml